    • rollback

      default boolean rollback(ProgressMonitor progressMonitor)
      Rolls back all the changes done by this instance of Supplier. The method can be called when a composite work was cancelled or one of participants failed and the result of the entire work shall be rolled back.
      Parameters:
      progressMonitor - Progress monitor to report the undo progress and possibly cancel the undo operation.
      Returns:
      ``true`` if the work was successfully rolled back or there was no work to roll back, ``false`` otherwise.
